%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20statement%2C%20a%20Wendy's%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20to%20me%20that%20the%20menu%20board%20would%20offer%20a%20variety%20of%20new%20features%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bdynamic%20pricing%2C%20different%20offerings%20in%20certain%20parts%20of%20the%20day%2C%20AI-enabled%20menu%20changes%2C%20and%20suggestive%20selling%20based%20on%20factors%20such%20as%20weather.%26quot%3B%20The%20move%20will%20let%20the%20company%20be%20%26quot%3Bcompetitive%20and%20flexible%26quot%3B%20with%20pricing%20and%20motivate%20customers%20to%20visit%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20will%20include%20discounts%20and%20value%20offers%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%2C%20predictably%2C%20has%20not%20gone%20over%20well%20with%20lovers%20of%20square%20burgers%20%E2%80%94%20or%20the%20internet%20at%20large.%20Many%20people%20aren't%20thrilled%20at%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20Frosty%20costing%20extra%20because%20it's%20hot%20outside%20and%20everybody%20else%20is%20also%20jonesing%20for%20a%20cool%2C%20sweet%20treat%20or%20waiting%20in%20line%20for%20some%20nuggets%20and%20suddenly%20seeing%20the%20price%20change%20when%20they're%20next%20at%20the%20register.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20doubt%20Wendy's%20could%20have%20done%20a%20better%20job%20with%20the%20rollout%20here.%20The%20talk%20on%20the%20earnings%20call%20comes%20off%20as%20some%20vague%20technobabble%20focused%20on%20maximizing%20profits%2C%20which%20makes%20sense%20given%20that%20executives%20were%20talking%20to%20investors.%20In%20a%20different%20world%2C%20you%20could%20imagine%20the%20company%20laying%20this%20out%20as%20a%20win%20for%20consumers%3A%20%26quot%3BCome%20on%20in%20and%20get%20a%20discount%20on%20your%20favorite%20Wendy's%20sandwich%20when%20business%20is%20slow.%26quot%3B%20That%20is%20not%2C%20however%2C%20the%20route%20it%20took%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20what's%20coming%20back%20to%20bite%20the%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnee-jerk%20reaction%20an