n%20on%20an%20earnings%20call%20makes%20sense%20in%20a%20vacuum%20%E2%80%94%20investors%20want%20them%20to%20show%20progress%20on%20their%20digital%20efforts%2C%20and%20they%20like%20the%20idea%20of%20bigger%20order%20sizes.%20But%20what's%20said%20in%20an%20earnings%20call%20doesn't%20always%20stay%20in%20an%20earnings%20call.%20And%20it's%20also%20worth%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20people%20who%20are%20going%20to%20bear%20the%20brunt%20of%20consumer%20ire%20at%20Wendy's%20aren't%20the%20executives%20announcing%20the%20move%20or%20the%20investors%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20woo%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20the%20employees%20who%20are%20going%20to%20have%20to%20explain%20why%20a%20chicken%20sandwich%20just%20got%20%241.50%20more%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Wendy's%20has%20made%20an%20unforced%20error%20and%20has%20a%20real%20public-relations%20kerfuffle%20on%20its%20hands.%20Consumers%20are%20already%20wary%20of%20dynamic%20pricing%2C%20and%20they%20see%20the%20downsides%20more%20than%20the%20upsides.%20It's%20annoying%20enough%20when%20you%20try%20to%20order%20an%20Uber%20after%20a%20long%20night%20and%20are%20confronted%20with%20an%20eye-popping%20price.%20Now%2C%20imagine%20it%20at%20the%20fast-food%20counter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20come%202025%2C%20that%20Wendy's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wendys.com%2Fblog%2Fwendys-breakfast-and-biggie-bag-specials%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%245%20Biggie%20Bag%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20cost%20you%20%244.50%20or%20%245.50%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20time%20of%20day.%20Whether%20this%20is%20a%20brave%20new%20world%20in%20fast%20food%20or%20a%20blip%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20Whatever%20the%20case%2C%20sir%20(or%20ma'am)%2C%20this%20will%20be%20a%20Wendy's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%