%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMost%20of%20our%20clients%20don't%20have%20the%20time%20or%20patience%20to%20play%20the%20%26quot%3BHerm%C3%A8s%C2%A0game%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHerm%C3%A8s%20bags%20are%20sold%20to%20clients%20who%20consistently%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fhow-to-buy-a-birkin-bag%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Espend%20the%20most%20on%20the%20brand%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Customers%20must%20cultivate%20a%20relationship%20with%20their%20Herm%C3%A8s%20sales%20associate%20by%20purchasing%20all%20sorts%20of%20Herm%C3%A8s%20items%20other%20than%20leather%20%E2%80%94%20fine%20jewelry%2C%20watches%2C%20and%20furniture%20have%20the%20greatest%20benefit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20some%20point%2C%20your%20sales%20associate%20will%20offer%20you%20a%20bag%2C%20but%20it's%20unlikely%20to%20be%20the%20bag%20you%20want%20and%20you%20may%20have%20to%20wait%20a%20long%20time%20for%20another%20opportunity.%20Herm%C3%A8s%20also%20limits%20the%20purchases%20of%20Birkins%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkylie-jenner-sorella-sky-blue-mock-neck-zippered-dress-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EKellys%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20other%20quota%20bags%20to%20two%20a%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20of%20our%20clients%20prefer%20to%20come%20to%20us%20and%20get%20exactly%20what%20they%20want%20the%20same%20day%20without%20waiting%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20why%20our%20bags%20sell%20at%20a%20premium%20to%20Herm%C3%A8s'%20retail%20price.%20We%20get%20rare%20bags%20because%20we've%20spent%20many%20years%20cultivating%20relationships%20with%20clients%20and%20VIPs%2C%20and%20they%20know%20we're%20discreet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHerm%C3%A8s%20and%20Chanel%20bags%20increase%20in%20price%20every%20year%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20resale%20world%2C%20the%20price%20of%20bags%20is%20a%20bit%20arbitrary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20A%20Herm%C3%A8s%20Kelly%20bag%20may%20cost%20%2410%2C900%20in%20the%20store%2C%20but%20it%20sells%20on%20the%20secondary%20market%20for%20%2436%2C000%20because%20the%20demand%20outweighs%20the%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20used%20to%20limit%20credit%20card%20purchases%20to%20%2450%2C000%20and%20offered%20bank%20wire%20options%2C%20but%20we%20changed%20it%20to%20%24100%2C000.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWithin%20three%20days%2C%20someone%20bought%20a%20crocodile%20Birkin%20for%20%2497%2C570.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20priciest%20bags%20we've%20ever%20sold%20was%20a%20Himalaya%20Birkin%20with%20diamonds%20for%20%24525%2C000.%20Several%20clients%20have%20spent%20more%20than%20%241%20million.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20crocodile%20print%20Birkin%20bag%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65de335d90413ab8e1d7331c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Himalaya%20Birkin%20bag%20that%20sold%20for%20%24525%2C000.%3Cp%3EMadison%20Avenue%20Couture%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20have%20people%20who%20try%20to%20sell%20us%20their%20fakes%20whether%20they%20know%20it%20or%20not%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20this%20business%20evolved%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuperfake-handbags-clothing-almost-real-knockoffs-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20counterfeiters%C2%A0have%2C%C2%A0too%3C%2Fa%3E.%20About%203%25%20of%20the%20bags%20submitted%20to%20us%20are%20counterfeit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndividuals%2C%20other%20resellers%2C%20and%20boutiques%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%20sell%20their%20bags%20to%20us.%20We%20have%20a%20double-authentication%20process%20and%20never%20pay%20before%20we%20authenticate%20the%20item%20by%20a%20third%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20uncomfortable%20to%20tell%20a%20wife%20or%20girlfriend%20that%20the%20bag%20their%20significant%20other%20gave%20them%20wasn't%20what%20they%20thought.%20It's%20sad%20to%20see%20someone's%20genuine%20reaction%20when%20they%20realize%20they've%20been%20lied%20to%20or%20misled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20are%20over%20a%20dozen%20places%20on%20bags%20to%20look%20for%20consistencies%20to%20determine%20if%20a%20luxury%20item%20like%20a%20Herm%C3%A8s%20bag%20is%20real%20or%20not%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20spotting%20fakes%2C%20stamps%2C%20maker's%20marks%2C%20and%20overall%20construction%20are%20great%20places%20to%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20consumer%2C%20I%20would%20focus%20on%20these%20details%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Overall%20quality%20of%20the%20bag%20and%20its%20construction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHerm%C3%A8s%20uses%20the%20highest%20quality%20materials%2C%20and%20the%20bags%20are%20made%20by%20master%20craftspeople%20who%20have%20been%20trained%20for%20years.%C2%A0If%20the%20bag%20looks%20like%20it's%20been%20made%20with%20cheaper%20materials%20or%20hardware%20or%20has%20been%20sloppily%20put%20together%2C%20it's%20not%20an%20authentic%20Herm%C3%A8s%20bag.%C2%A0Sometimes%20the%20grain%20on%20the%20leather%20is%20wrong%2C%20the%20bag%20feels%20lighter%20than%20a%20real%20Herm%C3%A8s%20bag%2C%20or%20the%20hardware%20is%20too%20thin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Front%20hardware%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hardware%20on%20the%20left%20strap%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-the-iconic-hermes-birkin-handbag-was-invented-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBirkin%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Kelly%20is%20engraved%20with%20HERMES_PARIS.%C2%A0The%20font%20must%20be%20consistent%20with%20the%20font%20used%20by%20Herm%C3%A8s.%C2%A0Often%20the%20'A'%20can't%20be%20properly%20duplicated%20or%20the%20hyphen%20is%20wrong%2C%20or%20the%20accent%20over%20the%20second%20'e'%20in%20Herm%C3%A8s%20is%20off.%C2%A0Under%20a%20loupe%2C%20the%20engraving%20may%20look%20chiseled%20and%20not%20as%20smooth%20as%20a%20genuine%20Herm%C3%A8s%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Front%20stamp%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stamp%20on%20the%20leather%20under%20the%20flap%20of%20a%20Birkin%20and%20Kelly%20has%20a%20certain%20consistency.%C2%A0The%20letters%20are%20spaced%20equally%20apart%20and%20the%20same%20height%20on%20each%20line.%20If%20the%20bag%20is%20a%20Horseshoe%20stamp%20bag%2C%20which%20is%20a%20custom%20order%2C%20or%20an%20exotic%2C%20there's%20a%20symbol%2C%20and%20on%20fake%20bags%2C%20it's%20often%20improperly%20placed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Stitching%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIndividual%20craftsmen%20make%20these%20bags%2C%20so%20the%20stitching%20is%20imperfect.%20They%20use%20a%20method%20called%20saddle%20stitching%20with%20a%20specific%20upwards%20flow.%20If%20the%20stitching%20is%20consistent%20and%20looks%20machine-made%2C%20then%20it's%20not%20made%20by%20one%20of%20those%20skilled%20artists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Sizing%20and%20proportion%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20model%20is%20a%20specific%20size%20%E2%80%94%20so%20if%20you%20measure%20the%20bag%20and%20it%20isn't%20those%20specific%20measurements%2C%20it's%20definitely%20a%20fake.%C2%A0Sometimes%20on%20fakes%2C%20the%20base%20is%20short%2C%20but%20given%20the%20geometric%C2%A0construction%20of%20the%20bags%2C%C2%A0especially%20the%20Sellier%20ones%2C%20a%20short%20base%20will%20need%20to%20have%20shorter%20sides%20to%20maintain%20proportion%2C%20and%20it's%20no%20longer%20a%20size%20that%20Herm%C3%A8s%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%C2%A0Zipper%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Birkin%20and%20Kelly%2C%20there's%20a%20zippered%20compartment.%C2%A0The%20pull%20is%20stamped%20Herm%C3%A8s%20and%20there's%20an%20'H'%20at%20the%20other%20end.%C2%A0Most%20fakes%20can't%C2%A0replicate%20the%20zipper%20pull%20and%2For%20'H'%20to%20the%20level%20of%20an%20authentic%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Keys%20and%20lock%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lock%20and%20the%20keys%20have%20matching%20numbers%2C%20but%20some%20numbers%20have%20been%20consistent%20with%20counterfeits.%C2%A0The%20engraving%20on%20the%20lock%20must%20be%20smooth%20and%20not%20chiseled%20or%20dotted.%20If%20it's%20not%20smooth%2C%20the%20lock%20is%20fake%2C%20and%20the%20handbag%20likely%20is%20also.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E8.%20Serial%20code%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20Herm%C3%A8s%20bag%20has%20a%20serial%20code%20inside%20the%20bag.%C2%A0The%20first%20letter%20denotes%20the%20year%20the%20bag%20was%20made.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20code%20consists%20of%20identifiers%20placed%20in%20a%20certain%20location%20in%20the%20bag%20with%20certain%20spacing.%20If%20they're%20in%20a%20different%20location%20or%20look%20inconsistent%20in%20spacing%20or%20lettering%2C%20that's%20a%20red%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E9.%20Dustbag%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202005%2C%20the%20Herm%C3%A8s%20dustbag%20has%20been%20a%20beige%20herringbone%20made%20of%20high-quality%20material%20with%20a%20brown%20drawstring.%C2%A0In%20the%20front%20center%20is%20the%20Herm%C3%A8s%20%26quot%3BLe%20Duc%26quot%3B%20logo%20surrounded%20by%20two%20circles.%C2%A0If%20there's%20one%20circle%2C%20or%20if%20the%20Le%20Duc%20is%20too%20dark%20or%20off-center%2C%20the%20dustbag%20is%20likely%20fake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E10.%20Color%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHerm%C3%A8s%20introduces%20or%20reintroduces%20certain%20colors%20yearly%20and%20discontinues%20or%20%26quot%3Brests%26quot%3B%20other%20colors.%20Sometimes%20a%20color%20will%20be%20available%20in%20one%20leather%20and%20not%20another.%C2%A0If%20a%20bag%20is%20of%20a%20color%20or%20in%20a%20leather%20that%20wasn't%20produced%20in%20the%20year%20it%20says%20it%20was%2C%20it's%20unlikely%20to%20be%20a%20genuine%20Herm%C3%A8s%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E11.%20Smell%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHerm%C3%A8s%20uses%20the%20finest%20leather%2C%20so%20the%20bag%20shouldn't%20smell%20of%20plastic%20or%20have%20an%20overpowering%20chemical%20smell.%20It%20should%20smell%20like%20rich%20leather.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E12.%20Receipt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECounterfeiters%20have%20been%20known%20to%20alter%20authentic%20receipts.%C2%A0We%20keep%20a%20book%20of%20legitimate%20receipts%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%20to%20compare%20and%20ensure%20they're%20consistent.%20All%20receipts%20from%20the%20same%20boutique%20use%20a%20particular%20font.%C2%A0They're%20typically%20packed%20with%20important%20information%20regarding%20the%20bag%2C%20color%2C%20hardware%2C%20size%2C%20and%20serial%20code.%C2%A0If%20the%20font%20or%20information%20differs%2C%20it's%20a%20major%20red%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E13.%20Price%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20price%20is%20too%20good%20to%20be%20true%2C%20then%20it%20is.%20There%20are%20no%20deals%20%E2%80%94%20if%20someone%20offers%20a%20new%20Herm%C3%A8s%20bag%20below%20market%20in%20the%20secondary%20market%2C%20I'd%20recommend%20staying%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-hermes-bag-fake-purse-resale-counterfeit-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709114701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65de18266080194819fa7bea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-hermes-bag-fake-purse-resale-counterfeit-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20buying%20and%20selling%20Herm%C3%A8s%20bags%20for%20a%20decade%2C%20Alexis%20Clarbour%20knows%20how%20to%20tell%20a%20real%20bag%20from%20a%20fake%20purse.%20Authenticity%20is%20crucial.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider