ws%2F002D%2Fproduction%2F_132754000_capture.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68415802%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Construction%20pictures%20suggest%20the%20cladding%20used%20on%20the%20building%20may%20be%20of%20a%20type%20now%20banned%20in%20the%20UK.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68415802%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68415802.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68415802.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2214-Month%20Wait%2C%20Then%20Strike%3A%20Himachal%20Royals%20Open%20New%20Front%20For%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVirbhadra%20Singh%2C%20Congress's%20tallest%20leader%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20a%20six-time%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20breathed%20his%20last%20on%20July%208%2C%202021.%20But%20the%20Congress%20fought%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20a%20year%20a%20later%20not%20in%20the%20name%20of%20any%20living%20leader%2C%20but%20in%20the%20name%20of%20its%20dead%20veteran.%20There%20were%20faultlines%2C%20of%20course.%20The%20state%20Congress%20was%20helmed%20by%20Virbhadra%20Singh's%20wife%20Pratibha%20Singh%20and%20leading%20the%20party's%20campaign%20committee%20was%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%2C%20a%20grassroots-level%20leader%20and%20a%20known%20critic%20of%20the%20late%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leadership%2C%20however%2C%20managed%20to%20project%20a%20united%20front%20and%20the%20party%20won%2040%20seats%20out%20of%20the%2068%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20ousting%20the%20incumbent%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bigger%20challenge%2C%20however%2C%20was%20waiting.%20Pratibha%20Singh%20was%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20frontrunner%20for%20the%20top%20post%2C%20but%20the%20Congress%20decided%20to%20bet%20on%20Mr%20Sukhu.%20Reluctantly%2C%20the%20mother-son%20duo%20of%20Pratibha%20Singh%20and%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20swallowed%20defeat.%20Fourteen%20months%20on%2C%20as%20Mr%20Sukhu%20fights%20to%20save%20his%20government%20after%20dramatic%20developments%20during%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20knives%20are%20out.%20The%20seeds%20of%20discontent%20sown%20a%20year%20back%20have%20borne%20fruit%2C%20with%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20resigning%20as%20minister%20and%20accusing%20the%20government%20of%20Mr%20Sukhu%20of%20disrespecting%20his%20father%20despite%20the%20Congress%20winning%20the%20polls%20in%20his%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Royal%20Veteran%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20scion%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20royal%20family%20of%20Bushahr%2C%20Virbhadra%20Singh%20was%20fondly%20called%20Raja%20Sahib.%20An%20alumnus%20of%20the%20prestigious%20Bishop%20Cotton%20School%20in%20Shimla%20and%20Delhi's%20St%20Stephen's%20College%2C%20he%20became%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%201962.%20He%20would%20get%20elected%20to%20the%20Lower%20House%20of%20Parliament%20four%20more%20times.%20Following%20two%20stints%20as%20a%20central%20minister%2C%20he%20became%20Chief%20Minister%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%201983.%20He%20would%20go%20on%20to%20occupy%20the%20post%20six%20times%20during%20his%20long%20political%20career.%20He%20lost%20the%20post%20in%202017%20when%20the%20BJP%20won%20the%20state%20polls%20and%20Jairam%20Thakur%20took%20over%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh's%20last%20years%20on%20the%20political%20landscape%20overlapped%20with%20Mr%20Sukhu's%20tenure%20as%20state%20Congress%20chief%20and%20there%20was%20no%20love%20lost%20between%20them.%20So%20much%20so%20that%20at%20one%20point%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20refused%20to%20share%20stage%20with%20Mr%20Sukhu.%20The%20leadership%20did%20manage%20a%20truce%20but%20the%20acrimony%20remained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Grassroots%20Leader%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20rise%20of%20Mr%20Sukhu%20was%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20that%20of%20Mr%20Singh.%20Coming%20from%20an%20ordinary%20family%2C%20he%20started%20out%20as%20an%20activist%20of%20the%20Congress's%20students%20wing%2C%20NSUI.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20councillor%20in%20Shimla%20municipal%20corporation%20before%20being%20elected%20to%20the%20Assembly%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202003.%20A%20four-time%20MLA%2C%20he%20took%20over%20as%20state%20Congress%20chief%20in%202019%2C%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20his%20rivalry%20with%20Virbhadra%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20towering%20stature%20of%20the%20six-time%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Mr%20Sukhu%20minced%20no%20words%20in%20his%20criticism%20of%20the%20veteran.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%202019%2C%20he%20hit%20out%20at%20Mr%20Singh%20for%20%26quot%3Bblackmailing%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20before%20every%20election.%20%26quot%3BSingh%20considers%20himself%20as%20Congress%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20The%20truth%20is%20that%20time%20has%20changed.%20Congress%20is%20strong%20at%20the%20booth%20level%20and%20Singh%20is%20not%20necessary%20for%20the%20Congress%20to%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress's%20Big%20Choice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20its%202022%20victory%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20faced%20with%20a%20tough%20choice%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post.%20It%20picked%20Mr%20Sukhu%20over%20Virbhadra%20Singh's%20wife%20Pratibha%20or%20son%20Vikramaditya%20Singh.%20There%20were%20reasons%20for%20this%20decision.%20The%20BJP's%20favourite%20line%20of%20attack%20on%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party%20is%20dynasty.%20In%20Mr%20Sukhu%2C%20the%20Congress%20saw%20a%20model%20party%20worker%20who%20had%20risen%20from%20the%20grassroots%20and%20had%20administrative%20experience.%20Choosing%20him%20would%20blunt%20the%20BJP%20charge%2C%20the%20Congress%20must%20have%20thought.%20The%20Congress%20leader%20is%20also%20known%20to%20be%20close%20to%20Congress%20leaders%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra.%20Also%2C%20choosing%20Mr%20Sukhu%20helped%20the%20Congress%20put%20the%20corruption%20charges%20against%20Virbhadra%20Singh%20behind%20them%20and%20closed%20another%20line%20of%20attack%20from%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20factor%20was%20that%20the%20Vibhadra%20Singh%20camp%20did%20not%20perform%20very%20well%20in%20the%202022%20polls%2C%20depriving%20them%20of%20the%20political%20muscle%20required%20to%20clinch%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Balancing%20Act%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20announcement%20of%20Mr%20Sukhu%20as%20the%20high%20command's%20Chief%20Minister%20choice%2C%20Pratibha%20Singh%20was%20being%20considered%20a%20frontrunner%20for%20the%20top%20post.%20When%20the%20Congress%20decided%20otherwise%2C%20it%20tried%20a%20balancing%20act%20to%20prevent%20a%20mutiny.%20The%20state%20Congress%20president%20post%20stayed%20with%20Pratibha%20Singh%20and%20her%20son%20Vikramditya%20was%20given%20a%20minister's%20post.%20%26quot%3BWe%20accept%20the%20decision%20taken%20by%20Congress%20high%20command%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20after%20the%20big%20announcement.%20Mr%20Sukhu%20ruled%20out%20any%20discontent%20in%20the%20Congress%20ranks%20following%20his%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Timely%20Strike%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Congress%20struggled%20to%20recover%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%20stunner%20pulled%20off%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20royals%20opened%20up%20another%20front.%20In%20a%20press%20conference%20this%20morning%2C%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20accused%20the%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20government%20of%20disrespecting%20his%20father%20and%20ignoring%20the%20voices%20of%20MLAs%20in%20its%2014-month%20rule.%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20resigned%20as%20minister%20and%20said%20that%20ball%20is%20in%20the%20Congress%20high%20command's%20court.%20This%2C%20after%20six%20Congress%20MLAs%20cross-voted%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%20and%20the%20BJP%20claimed%20that%20the%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20government%20had%20lost%20the%20mandate%20to%20stay%20in%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress'%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20has%20said%20that%20the%20leadership%20will%20not%20shy%20away%20from%20%26quot%3Bdifficult%20decisions%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIndividuals%20are%20not%20important%2C%20it's%20the%20mandate%20that%20we%20have%20to%20respect.%20All%20options%20are%20open%20and%20the%20party%20is%20supreme.%20We%20will%20take%20whatever%20decision%20is%20required%20and%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709114460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F2inmvl7_virbhadra-sukhu-split_625x300_28_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsukhvinder-singh-sukhu-himachal-congress-virbhadra-singh-14-month-wait-then-strike-himachal-royals-open-new-front-for-congress-5143207%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virbhadra%20Singh%2C%20Congress's%20tallest%20leader%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20a%20six-time%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20breathed%20his%20last%20on%20July%208%2C%202021.%20But%20Congress%20fought%20state%20polls%20a%20year%20a%20later%20not%20in%20the%20name%20of%20any%20living%20leader%2C%20but%20in%20the%20name%20of%20its%20dead%20veteran%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsukhvinder-singh-sukhu-himachal-congress-virbhadra-singh-14-month-wait-then-strike-himachal-royals-open-new-front-for-congress-5143207%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsukhvinder-singh-sukhu-himachal-congress-virbhadra-singh-14-month-wait-then-strike-himachal-royals-open-new-front-for-congress-5143207%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsu