0convicts%20in%202022%2C%20and%20with%20the%20Foreigners%20Regional%20Registration%20Office%20(FRRO)%2C%20Chennai%2C%20issuing%20an%20order%20to%20send%20him%20to%20Lanka%20on%20February%2023%2C%20in%20his%20favour%2C%20Santhan%20could%20not%20be%20sent%20home%20as%20ordained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanthan%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20Hepatology%20(liver)%20ICU%20of%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Government%20General%20Hospital%20(RGGGH)%20here%20on%20January%2028%20in%20a%20critical%20condition%20from%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Memorial%20Government%20Hospital%2C%20Tiruchirappalli%2C%20where%20he%20was%20undergoing%20treatment%20for%20cryptogenic%20cirrhosis%20-%20a%20condition%20with%20no%20apparent%20underlying%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20hospital%20here%20with%20breathlessness%2C%20fluid%20in%20the%20abdomen%20and%20swelling%20in%20the%20limbs.%20%26quot%3BHe%20suffered%20a%20setback%20in%20his%20condition%20on%20Tuesday%20night%20and%20early%20today%20he%20passed%20away%20after%20a%20cardiac%20arrest%2C%26quot%3B%20RGGGH%20dean%20Dr%20E%20Theranirajan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20A%20G%20Perarivalan%20was%20set%20at%20liberty%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20May%202022%2C%20Santhan%20and%20others%20were%20released%20in%20November%202022.%20All%20of%20them%20have%20been%20in%20prison%20for%20over%20three%20decades%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20former%20prime%20minister's%20assassination%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%20last%20year%2C%20he%20sought%20release%20from%20the%20special%20camp%20where%20he%20was%20lodged%20in%20Tiruchirappalli%20and%20reportedly%20said%20the%20jail%20was%20better%20than%20the%20room%20in%20the%20special%20camp%20for%20refugees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2013%2C%20the%20state%20government%20had%20informed%20the%20Madras%20High%20Court%20that%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20Deputy%20High%20Commission%20here%20had%20issued%20temporary%20travel%20document%20to%20Santhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobert%20Payas%2C%20Murugan%20alias%20Sriharan%20and%20Jayakumar%20were%20the%20others%20who%20were%20moved%20from%20the%20Vellore%20prison%20to%20the%20Tiruchirappalli%20special%20camp%20along%20with%20Santhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20ordered%20the%20premature%20release%20of%20Nalini%20Sriharan%20and%20another%20convict%2C%20RP%20Ravichandran%2C%20too.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709113920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Ffh1k7t2o_jail-generic-getty_625x300_20_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajiv-gandhi-case-convicts-last-wish-to-see-mother-remained-unfulfilled-5142772%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20last%20wish%20of%20Santhan%2C%20among%20the%20seven%20convicts%20released%20in%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20assassination%20case%2C%20to%20return%20to%20his%20home%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20take%20care%20of%20his%20aged%20mother%20never%20materialised.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajiv-gandhi-case-convicts-last-wish-to-see-mother-remained-unfulfilled-5142772%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajiv-gandhi-case-convicts-last-wish-to-see-mother-remained-unfulfilled-5142772%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajiv-gandhi-case-convicts-last-wish-to-see-mother-remained-unfulfilled-5142772%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akshay%20contributes%20Rs.%201%20crore%20to%20a%20hostel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709113810000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108071443%2Cimgsize-21802.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2