24%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGeneral%20Assembly%20chief%E2%80%99s%20alert%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20warnings%20that%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20and%20even%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Fcharter-united-nations%2Findex.html%5C%22%3EUN%20Charter%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20coming%20under%20increasing%20threat%20around%20the%20world%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%2C%20Mr.%20Francis%2C%20told%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20that%20it%20was%20time%20for%20all%20global%20citizens%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdo%20our%20part%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%2075%20years%20after%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Funiversal-declaration-human-rights%2F%5C%22%3EUniversal%20Declaration%20of%20Human%20Rights%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Chumanity%E2%80%99s%20cherished%20Magna%20Carta%E2%80%9D%20%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20%C2%A0conflict%20and%20the%20impact%20of%20climate%C2%A0change%20%E2%80%9Cincluding%20the%20existential%20threat%20of%20sea-level%20rise%E2%80%9D%20had%20left%20300%20million%20people%20in%20dire%20need%20of%20humanitarian%20assistance%2C%20some%20114%20million%20of%20them%20being%20refugees%20and%20other%20displaced%20people%2C%20he%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20must%20not%20simply%20stand%20by%20as%20callous%20observers%20lest%20we%20be%20seen%20as%20complicit%20in%20the%20expanding%20web%20of%20dehumanization%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20must%20do%20our%20part.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20crisis%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20President%20said%20that%20the%20suffering%20of%20innocent%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%20had%20reached%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunbearable%20tipping%20point%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E80%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20enclave%E2%80%99s%20population%20had%20been%20displaced%20and%20was%20now%20%E2%80%9Cteetering%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20starvation%20and%20trapped%20in%20the%20depths%20of%20an%20impending%20though%20avoidable%20public%20health%20catastrophe%E2%80%9D%2C%20Mr.%20Francis%20told%20the%20forum%E2%80%99s%2047%20Member%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20war%20continues%20in%20Gaza%2C%20triggered%20by%20Hamas-led%20attacks%20that%20left%20some%201%2C200%20dead%20and%20more%20than%20250%20taken%20hostage%20on%207%20October%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20most%20vulnerable%20suffer%20most%E2%80%9D%2C%20Mr.%20Francis%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CHostages%20and%20their%20families%20are%20living%20in%20anguish%2C%20women%20and%20children%20are%20facing%20desperate%20and%20uncertain%20futures%2C%20and%20innocent%20civilians%20are%20unjustly%20caught%20in%20life%20threatening%20crossfire.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20the%20name%20of%20humanity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20%E2%80%93%20not%20only%20in%20Gaza%20but%20in%20Haiti%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20Sudan%2C%20the%20wider%20Sahel%20and%20Yemen%20%E2%80%93%20the%20General%20Assembly%20President%20insisted%3A%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20must%20not%20fail%20the%20victims%20%E2%80%93%20the%20victims%20of%20human%20rights%20violations%E2%80%A6%20We%20must%20never%20tolerate%20or%20ignore%20the%20flagrant%20disregard%20for%20the%20rights%20and%20freedoms%20our%20forebearers%20worked%20so%20arduously%20to%20define%20and%20to%20codify.%20Nor%20should%20we%20ignore%20the%20systemic%20impunity%20with%20which%20it%20is%20perpetrated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20Francis%20also%20insisted%20on%20the%20need%20for%20an%20%E2%80%9Cimmediate%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%E2%80%9D%20in%20Gaza%20and%20for%20humanitarian%20corridors%20to%20deliver%20aid%20to%20some%201.5%20million%20homeless%20Palestinians%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20name%20of%20humanity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appeal%20by%20the%20President%20of%20the%20General%20Assembly%20came%20days%20after%20receiving%20a%20letter%20from%20the%20head%20of%20the%20UN%20agency%20for%20Palestinians%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unrwa.org%2F%5C%22%3EUNRWA%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20warning%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmonumental%20disaster%E2%80%9D%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%20amid%20repeated%20Israeli%20calls%20to%20dismantle%20it%20and%20the%20freezing%20of%20%24450%20million%20in%20funding%20by%20dozens%20of%20donors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20implore%C2%A0%20donor%20States%20to%20uphold%20and%20sustain%20their%20contributions%20to%20the%20critical%20funding%20necessary%20for%20UNRWA%20to%20discharge%20its%20mandated%20responsibilities%20to%20the%20Palestinians.%20Even%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20current%20extraordinary%20challenges%2C%20UNRWA%20has%20been%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20an%20indispensable%20lifeline%20of%20support%20to%20the%20Palestinians%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr.%20Francis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1146942%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20UN%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709112095000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28144500%2Fimage1170x530cropped-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwith-eyes-on-gaza-ukraine-un-chief-launches-rights-protection-pledge%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UN%20chief%20said%20that%20any%20further%20extension%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20ground%20operation%20in%20the%20south%20of%20Gaza%20%E2%80%9Cwould%20not%20only%20be%20terrifying%20for%20more%20than%20a%20million%20Palestinian%20civilians%20sheltering%20there%3B%20it%20would%20put%20the%20final%20nail%20in%20the%20coffin%20of%20our%20aid%20programmes%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwith-eyes-on-gaza-ukraine-un-chief-launches-rights-protection-pledge%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%