'demilitarized%20zone'%20has%20in%20many%20ways%20kept%20aggressive%20and%20war-mongering%20North%20Korea%20under%20control%20and%20the%20same%20could%20be%20true%20of%20this%20Middle%20Eastern%20alliance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWechsler%20said%20a%20DMZ%20could%20technically%20be%20created%20and%20administered%20by%20a%20coalition%20of%20Arab%20states%2C%20which%20wouldn't%20require%20a%20permanent%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20would%20only%20work%20if%20Israel%20agrees%20to%20a%20two-state%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Arab%20world%20has%20been%20remarkably%20clear%20that%20as%20a%20prerequisite%20to%20anything%20that%20they%20might%20do%20collectively%20in%20Gaza%2C%20they%20need%20to%20see%20from%20Israel%20a%20path%20to%20a%20Palestinian%20state%20that%20has%20a%20timeframe%20and%20is%20irreversible%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Wechsler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223387%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20holds%20up%20a%20marker%20and%20a%20map%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BNew%20Middle%20East.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ded57790413ab8e1d75576%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222259%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWeeks%20before%20the%20October%207%20attack%2C%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20presented%20the%20United%20Nations%20with%20a%20%26quot%3BNew%20Middle%20East%26quot%3B%20map.%3Cp%3ESpencer%20Platt%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20opposed%20the%20two-state%20solution.%20Ironically%2C%20the%20very%20concept%20of%20the%20two-state%20solution%20could%20extend%20his%20political%20life%2C%20said%20Lord.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20vast%20majority%20of%20Israelis%20want%20Bibi%20gone%20at%20the%20first%20opportunity%2C%20but%20Bibi%20can%20turn%20to%20an%20Israeli%20public%20that%20is%20shocked%20and%20traumatized%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhamas-goal-october-7-attack-israel-gaza-war-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHamas'%20October%207th%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20tell%20it%20that%20he%20alone%20can%20rebuff%20Washington's%20effort%20to%20build%20a%20'terrorist%20Arab%20state%20on%20our%20border%2C'%26quot%3B%20Lord%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJacobs%20agreed.%20%26quot%3BSome%20Arab%20countries%20might%20consider%20sending%20peacekeepers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20only%20as%20part%20of%20a%20credible%20political%20process%20working%20toward%20a%20two-state%20solution%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20this%20is%20something%20that%20the%20Israeli%20government%20rejects.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Hamas%20is%20removed%20from%20power%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20is%20left%20to%20rule%2C%20there%20are%20also%20questions%20as%20to%20whether%20its%20unpopular%20leader%2C%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%2C%20can%20effectively%20build%20the%20path%20to%20peace%2C%20Wechsler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mahmoud%20abbas%20palestine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5bb7ce7421e9cb66660123a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221327%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPalestinian%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas.%3Cp%3ESeth%20Wenig%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20see%2C%20given%20the%20lack%20of%20support%20for%20Abbas%20through%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20how%20an%20Abbas-led%20Palestinian%20Authority%20could%20be%20part%20of%20a%20two-state%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20Wechsler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20if%20Gaza%20continues%20to%20suffer%20under%20the%20heel%20of%20Israel's%20military%20and%20policies%2C%20Hamas%20will%20continue%20to%20fill%20its%20ranks%20with%20desperate%20Palestinians%2C%20Lord%20said.%20Creating%20a%20%26quot%3BMETO%26quot%3B%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bday-after%26quot%3B%20solution%20when