%2Fgadgets-news%2Fpakistani-hackers-deface-burger-singh-website-read-hackers-message-and-companys-response%2Farticleshow%2F108068183.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistani%20hacking%20group%20Team%20Insane%20PK%20targeted%20Burger%20Singh's%20website%2C%20leaving%20a%20digital%20graffiti%20wall.%20Burger%20Singh%20acknowledged%20the%20breach%20and%20expressed%20confidence%20in%20overcoming%20the%20momentary%20setback%2C%20maintaining%20a%20positive%20outlook%20for%20brand%20elevation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fpakistani-hackers-deface-burger-singh-website-read-hackers-message-and-companys-response%2Farticleshow%2F108068183.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22More%20Women%20May%20Be%20Psychopaths%20Than%20Previously%20Thought%2C%20Claims%20Expert%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20was%20commonly%20believed%20that%20most%20psychopaths%20are%20men%2C%20an%20expert%20suggests%20there%20might%20be%20way%20more%20women%20psychopaths%20than%20we%20thought.%20Recent%20studies%20indicate%20that%20male%20psychopaths%20may%20be%20overrepresented%20compared%20to%20females%2C%20at%20a%20ratio%20of%206%20to%201.%20Dr%20Clive%20Boddy%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20Anglia%20Ruskin%20University%20specialising%20in%20corporate%20psychopathy%2C%20challenges%20this%20ratio%2C%20suggesting%20it%20could%20be%20as%20low%20as%201.2%20to%201%2C%20potentially%20five%20times%20higher%20for%20females.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20generally%20attribute%20psychopathic%20characteristics%20to%20males%20rather%20than%20to%20females%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Boddy%20said%20in%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-mce-href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aru.ac.uk%2Fnews%2Ffemale-psychopaths-more-common-than-we-think%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aru.ac.uk%2Fnews%2Ffemale-psychopaths-more-common-than-we-think%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20even%20when%20females%20display%20some%20of%20the%20key%20traits%20associated%20with%20psychopathy%20-%20such%20as%20being%20insincere%2C%20deceitful%2C%20antagonistic%2C%20unempathetic%20and%20lacking%20in%20emotional%20depth%20-%20because%20these%20are%20seen%20as%20male%20characteristics%20they%20may%20not%20be%20labelled%20as%20such%2C%20even%20when%20they%20should%20be%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPsychopaths%20are%20commonly%20characterised%20by%20a%20lack%20of%20empathy%20and%20guilt%2C%20engaging%20in%20antisocial%20behaviour%2C%20frequent%20lying%2C%20and%20demonstrating%20traits%20of%20ruthlessness%2C%20narcissism%2C%20and%20manipulation.%20%E2%80%9CPsychopaths%20are%20after%20money%2C%20power%20and%20control%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr%20Boddy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20behaviour%20of%20female%20psychopaths%20seems%20to%20be%20subtle%20enough%20and%20less%20obvious%20than%20male%20psychopaths%20and%20therefore%20they're%20not%20recognised%20as%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Boddy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20small%20but%20mounting%20body%20of%20evidence%20describes%20female%20psychopaths%20as%20prone%20to%20expressing%20violence%20verbally%20rather%20than%20physically%2C%20with%20the%20violence%20being%20of%20a%20relational%20and%20emotional%20nature%2C%20more%20subtle%20and%20less%20obvious%20than%20that%20expressed%20by%20male%20psychopaths%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Boddy%20also%20pointed%20out%20a%20problem%20with%20a%20test%20for%20psychopathy%2C%20the%20Levenson%20self-report%20psychopathy%20scale%20(LSRP).%20He%20mentioned%20it%20seems%20to%20be%20more%20geared%20towards%20men.%20The%20first%20part%20looks%20at%20emotional%20detachment%2C%20selfishness%2C%20lack%20of%20empathy%2C%20and%20manipulation.%20But%20in%20the%20second%20part%2C%20which%20checks%20for%20the%20psychopathic%20lifestyle%2C%20the%20emphasis%20is%20on%20violence%20and%20antisocial%20behaviour%2C%20creating%20a%20gender-specific%20bias%20in%20psychopathy%20assessments.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20secondary%20element%2C%20and%20the%20measures%20for%20it%2C%20were%20largely%20based%20on%20studies%20of%20criminals%20who%20were%20in%20jail%20at%20the%20time%20and%20psychopathic%20-%20so%20the%20feeling%20is%2C%20among%20researchers%20these%20days%2C%20that%20those%20measures%20are%20just%20not%20suited%20to%20identifying%20female%20psychopathy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Boddy%20mentions%20that%20female%20psychopaths%20use%20deceit%20and%20seduction%20more%20than%20male%20psychopaths%20to%20gain%20social%20and%20financial%20advantages.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFemale%20psychopaths%2C%20while%20not%20as%20severely%20psychopathic%20or%20as%20psychopathic%20as%20often%20as%20males%20are%2C%20have%20nevertheless%20been%20underestimated%20in%20their%20incidence%20levels%20and%20are%20therefore%20more%20of%20a%20potential%20threat%20to%20business%20and%20society%20than%20anyone%20previously%20suspected.%20This%20has%20implications%20for%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%20because%20current%20risk%20management%20decisions%20involving%20partners%20and%20children%20may%20be%20faulty.%20It%20also%20has%20implications%20for%20organisational%20leadership%20selection%20decisions%20because%20female%20leaders%20cannot%20automatically%20be%20assumed%20to%20be%20more%20honest%2C%20caring%20and%20concerned%20with%20issues%20such%20as%20corporate%20social%20responsibility.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Clive%20Boddy%20has%20been%20studying%20the%20influence%20of%20psychopaths%20in%20the%20workplace%20since%202005.%20He%20is%20a%20leading%20academic%20in%20the%20field%2C%20having%20published%20extensively%20on%20corporate%20psychopathy.%20His%20research%20focuses%20on%20toxic%20leadership%2C%20specifically%20examining%20how%20corporate%20psychopaths%20affect%20employees%2C%20organisations%2C%20and%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22