A%22Manipur%20Assembly%20Session%20Begins%20Amid%20Tight%20Security%3B%20Previous%20Session%20Had%20Lasted%2011%20Minutes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07195859%2Fmanipur_assembly_session_2_20150625_1176793276.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Amid%20tight%20security%2C%20the%20winter%20session%20of%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%20began%20Wednesday%2C%20February%2028%2C%20in%20Imphal.%20This%20is%20the%20second%20time%20the%20House%20has%20met%20since%20ethnic%20violence%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-reasons-failure-and-solution-q-and-a%5C%22%3Ebroke%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20north-eastern%20state%20in%20May%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20previous%20session%2C%20held%20on%20August%2029%2C%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-assemblys-one-day-session-adjourned-after-11-minutes%5C%22%3Eended%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20just%20eleven%20minutes%20of%20business.%20Neither%20the%2010%20Kuki%20MLAs%20nor%20the%20majority%20of%20the%2010%20Naga%20MLAs%20took%20part%20in%20that%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20session%20had%20ended%20without%20putting%20on%20record%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20that%20had%20led%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20so%20many%20MLAs%20from%20the%20House.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20session%20turned%20into%20an%20exercise%20by%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20merely%20to%20keep%20the%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%20in%20Manipur%20at%20bay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20constitutional%20norm%2C%20a%20state%20assembly%20has%20to%20be%20in%20session%20every%20six%20months%2C%20unless%20there%20is%20direct%20central%20rule%20in%20that%20state%20due%20to%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20or%20some%20other%20pressing%20reason.%20Prior%20to%20the%20August%20session%2C%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-assembly-monsoon-session-anusuiya-uikey%5C%22%3Ehad%20met%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20March%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20too%2C%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20Manipur%20out%20of%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%2C%20a%20session%20had%20to%20be%20held%20within%20the%20last%20week%20of%20February.%20As%20per%20the%20Speaker%E2%80%99s%20announcement%2C%20the%20winter%20session%20will%20go%20on%20until%20March%205.%20It%E2%80%99ll%20have%20a%20total%20number%20of%20five%20sittings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20only%20one%20Kuki%20MLA%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Speaker%20seeking%20leave%20of%20absence%20from%20the%20session%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20nine%20MLAs%20from%20the%20community%2C%20too%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20skip%20it.%20The%20MLA%20who%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Speaker%20a%20day%20before%20the%20session%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-one-kuki-mla-seeks-leave%5C%22%3EHaokholet%20Kipgen%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20represents%20the%20Kuki-dominated%20Saitu%20constituency%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Kangpokpi%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20yet%20clear%20how%20many%20among%20the%2010%20Naga%20MLAs%20will%20attend%20the%20current%20session.%20On%20February%2023%2C%20an%20informal%20meeting%20of%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Naga%20MLAs%20had%20taken%20place%20in%20Guwahati.%20Since%20it%20was%20a%20closed%20door%20meeting%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20yet%20what%20exactly%20was%20discussed%20in%20it.%20However%2C%20a%20Kuki%20leader%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20said%20attempts%20were%20made%20by%20some%20Naga%20leaders%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20Centre%20to%20break%20the%20ice%20between%20the%20Kuki%20legislators%20and%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20so%20that%20they%20attend%20the%20current%20session%20and%20also%20help%20find%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20ongoing%20Manipur%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20a%20Kuki%20MLA%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20Paolienlal%20Haokip%2C%20got%20angry%20as%20the%20meeting%20was%20not%20to%20take%20%3Cem%3E(sic)%3C%2Fem%3E%20any%20concrete%20decision%20on%20a%20separate%20administration%20for%20the%20Kukis%2C%20and%20he%20eventually%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20person%20cited%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20earlier%20assembly%20session%2C%20Haokip%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanipur-as-violence-rages-on-mlas-divided-over-whether-or-not-to-hold-special-assembly-session%5C%22%3Ehad%20told%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWho%20would%20give%20assurance%20of%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20the%20Kuki%20MLAs%20going%20to%20Imphal%20to%20attend%20the%20assembly%20session%3F%20At%20this%20point%2C%20I%20would%20say%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20and%20also%20not%20necessary%20to%20participate%20in%20it%20as%20the%20separation%20of%20the%20state%20is%20complete.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ESangai%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20soon%20after%20the%20February%2023%20Guwahati%20meeting%2C%20a%20Naga%20MLA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesangaiexpress.com%2FEncyc%2F2024%2F2%2F24%2FBy-Our-Staff-ReporterIMPHAL-Feb-23-With-the-fifth-session-of-the-12th-State-Legislative-Assembly-set-to-b.html%5C%22%3Ehad%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CChief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20has%20knowledge%20of%20them%20(the%20Naga%20MLAs)%20attending%20the%20meeting.%20%3Cem%3E(sic)%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20coinciding%20with%20the%20start%20of%20the%20session%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20powerful%20civil%20society%20group%20from%20the%20Meitei%20community%2C%20COCOMI%2C%20or%20the%20Coordinating%20Committee%20on%20Manipur%20Integrity%2C%20has%20asked%20all%20women%20groups%20of%20the%20valley%20areas%20to%20stage%20a%20protest%20for%20an%20hour%20during%20the%20day%20in%20their%20locality%2C%20and%20to%20wear%20red%20outfits%20and%20carry%20out%20a%20torch%20rally%20each%20in%20the%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20COCOMI%20protest%20is%20aimed%20at%20pushing%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20to%20not%20renew%20the%20suspension%20of%20operation%20agreement%20with%20the%20Kuki%20armed%20groups.%20On%20February%2029%2C%20the%20six-month%20extension%20of%20the%20ceasefire%20with%20the%20Kuki%20groups%20will%20come%20up%20for%20an%20extension%20with%20the%20MHA.%20The%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20has%20already%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20ceasefire%20last%20year%2C%20weeks%20before%20the%20ethnic%20strife%20unfolded%20between%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20the%20Kukis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECOCOMI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fcocomi-proposes-protests-in-keithels%5C%22%3Ehas%20also%20submitted%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20memorandum%20to%20the%20MHA%20seeking%20an%20end%20to%20the%20extension%20of%20the%20ceasefire%20agreement%20with%20the%20Kuki%20groups.%20Note%20that%20the%20Centre%20is%20in%20peace%20talks%20with%20the%20Kuki%20groups.%20The%20argument%20of%20the%20Meitei%20group%20has%20been%20that%20Kuki%20militants%20have%20been%20breaking%20the%20suspension%20of%20operation%20agreement%20and%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20ethnic%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20last%20week%E2%80%99s%20arson%20at%20various%20offices%20of%20civil%20society%20groups%20in%20Imphal%2C%20the%20COCOMI%20office%20was%20also%20torched.%20Calling%20the%20incidents%20unfortunate%2C%20COCOMI%20coordinator%20Somorendra%20Thokchom%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesangaiexpress.com%2FEncyc%2F2024%2F2%2F28%2FBy-Our-Staff-ReporterIMPHAL-Feb-27-With-Assembly-session-all-set-to-begin-the-Coordinating-Committee-on.html%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20reporters%20in%20Imphal%2C%20on%20February%2027%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20more%20disappo