motional%20people.%20We%20don't%20care%20about%20posts.%20But%20a%20sense%20of%20respect%20that%20should%20be%20there...%20they%20could%20not%20do%20it%20despite%20repeated%20requests.%20It%20is%20very%20unfortunate.%20I%20am%20hurt%2C%20not%20politically%2C%20but%20emotionally.%20I%20do%20not%20know%20why%20it%20happened.%20I%20raised%20this%20issue%20with%20the%20party%20high%20command%2C%20but%20nothing%20happened.%20They%20should%20look%20into%20this.%20The%20people%20of%20Himachal%20are%20very%20emotional.%20Not%20everything%20can%20be%20seen%20through%20the%20prism%20of%20politics.%20As%20a%20son%2C%20I%20felt%20bad%20and%20I%20hope%20the%20party%20will%20take%20note%20of%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20firefighting%20a%20crisis%20in%20Himachal%20after%20six%20of%20its%20MLAs%20cross-voted%20in%20the%20election%20for%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat.%20The%20MLAs%20were%20later%20whisked%20away%20to%20a%20resort%20in%20Haryana's%20Panchkula%20and%20the%20BJP%20has%20now%20claimed%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20lost%20the%20mandate%20to%20stay%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%2C%20which%20has%2040%20MLAs%20in%20the%2068-member%20Assembly%2C%20has%20now%20rushed%20senior%20leaders%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%20and%20DK%20Shivakumar%20to%20Himachal%20for%20damage%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20recent%20political%20point%20of%20view%20of%20the%20developments%20that%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20can%20be%20said%20that%20the%20state%20government%20has%20lost%20the%20moral%20right%20to%20stay%20in%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Jairam%20Thakur%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709106600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Focp5oha_vikramaditya-singh_625x300_28_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsukhvinder-singh-sukhu-himachal-congress-vikramaditya-singh-d