me%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fuday-chopra-says-using-fairness-cream-is-not-a-race-issue-its-about-self-esteem-1681713%5C%22%3Efairness%20creams%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year.%20The%20overall%20skincare%20industry%20in%20India%20is%20pegged%20at%20Rs%2015%2C800%20crore%20in%202023.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsushant-singh-rajput-just-refused-a-fairness-cream-ad-deal-worth-15-crore-reports-1799151%5C%22%3EFairness%20creams%3C%2Fa%3E%20currently%20hold%20approximately%2025%25%20of%20the%20skincare%20market%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoes%20this%20signify%20a%20shift%20away%20from%20the%20obsession%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-year-jail-rs-50-lakh-fine-for-advertisements-for-fair-skin-government-proposes-2176292%5C%22%3Efair%20skin%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Or%20is%20it%20something%20else%3F%20To%20analyse%20this%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20to%20delve%20into%20the%20magnitude%20of%20the%20fairness%20cream%20industry%20and%20the%20kind%20of%20patronage%20it%20enjoys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20Obsession%20With%20Fairness%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETriggered%20during%20the%20rule%20of%20the%20Caucasian%20British%20and%20further%20perpetuated%20by%20class%20divisions%2C%20the%20preference%20for%20fair%20skin%20became%20deeply%20entrenched%20in%20the%20psyche%20of%20the%20Indian%20populace.%20This%20preference%20had%20originally%20led%20to%20the%20use%20of%20bleaching%20products.%20However%2C%20the%20Indian%20market%20-%20more%20particularly%2C%20women%20-%20had%20been%20eagerly%20waiting%20for%20a%20skincare%20product%20that%20would%20help%20them%20meet%20the%20societal%20ideal%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98fair%20bride'%2C%20often%20advertised%20in%20matrimonial%20columns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201975%2C%20Hindustan%20Unilever%20Ltd%20(HUL)%20responded%20to%20this%20demand%20by%20introducing%20%E2%80%98Fair%20%26amp%3B%20Lovely'%2C%20promoted%20as%20a%20safe%20alternative%20to%20bleaching.%20This%20face%20cream%2C%20promising%20fairer%20skin%20in%20six%20weeks%2C%20resonated%20with%20women%20fixated%20on%20lighter%20skin%20tones%20and%20quickly%20became%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20the%20Indian%20cosmetic%20market.%20Subsequently%2C%20numerous%20other%20brands%2C%20such%20as%20Emami%2C%20L'Or%C3%A9al%2C%20Ponds%2C%20and%20Neutrogena%2C%20entered%20the%20segment%20with%20their%20own%20offerings%20with%20products%20that%20emphasised%20anti-tanning%20and%20anti-pollution%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelevision%20commercials%20in%20the%201980s%20furthered%20discriminatory%20messages%2C%20suggesting%20that%20darker-skinned%20individuals%20faced%20challenges%20in%20securing%20employment%20or%20marriage%20proposals%20unless%20they%20attained%20fairness%20through%20the%20use%20of%20these%20creams.%20After%20facing%20significant%20criticism%2C%20Fair%20%26amp%3B%20Lovely%20underwent%20a%20rebranding%20effort%20to%20focus%20on%20women's%20empowerment%2C%20and%20ultimately%20renamed%20its%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98Glow%20and%20Lovely'.%20This%20was%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESomething%20For%20Men%2C%20Too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20touched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fbusiness%2Fnews%2Fthe-growing-market-of-men-s-fairness-cream-36568%5C%22%3Emen%20as%20well%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20Emami%20in%202005%20launching%20%E2%80%98Fair%20and%20Handsome'%2C%20the%20first%20fairness%20cream%20for%20men%2C%20followed%20by%20HUL's%20Glow%20%26amp%3B%20Handsome.%20The%20endorsement%20of%20skin-whitening%20creams%20by%20A-list%20Bollywood%20stars%20further%20strengthened%20the%20notion%20that%20beauty%20meant%20fairness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20noticeable%20shift%20from%20the%20pursuit%20of%20%E2%80%98fairness'%20to%20%E2%80%98glow'%20among%20millennials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20millennials%20are%20a%20wide-swathe%20generation.%20Attitudes%20in%20this%20generation%20have%20changed%20with%20gusto%20on%20many%20categories%20of%20consumption.%20The%20fairness%20cream%20is%20the%20first%20that%20was%20hit.%20Both%20the%20physical%20and%20political%20incorrectness%20of%20the%20category%20has%20hit%20consumption%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Harish%20Bijoor%2C%20Brand%20Guru%20%26amp%3B%20Founder%2C%20Harish%20Bijoor%C2%A0Consults%C2%A0Inc.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBijoor%20further%20adds%3A%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20have%20moved%20from%20fairness%20creams%20to%20skin-glow%20creams.%20Eventually%2C%20even%20skin-glow%20shall%20pass%20the%20mantle%20over%20to%20natural%20skincare%20serums.%20Expect%20loss%20in%20the%20share%20of%20the%20fairness%20cream%20market%20in%20the%20near%20to%20medium%20term%20for%20sure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EBreaking%20Stereotypes%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncreasing%20awareness%20has%20prompted%20a%20shift%20in%20the%20narrative%20around%20fairness.%20Initiatives%20such%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Dark%20Is%20Beautiful'%20campaign%2C%20launched%20in%202009%20by%20the%20Indian%20NGO%20Women%20of%20Worth%20and%20championed%20by%20Bollywood%20actor%20Nandita%20Das%2C%20aim%20to%20challenge%20stereotypes%20associated%20with%20fairness.%20In%202014%2C%20India%20banned%20%E2%80%98colourist'%20advertising%2C%20prohibiting%20the%20depiction%20of%20darker-skinned%20individuals%20in%20a%20negative%20light.%20Social%20media%20activism%2C%20coupled%20with%20global%20discussions%20on%20racism%20following%20events%20such%20as%20the%20death%20of%20George%20Floyd%20in%202020%2C%20have%20also%20contributed%20to%20changing%20mindsets.%20In%20response%20to%20mounting%20criticism%2C%20consumer%20brands%20like%20HUL%20have%20removed%20labels%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98fair'%2C%20%E2%80%98white'%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98light'%20from%20their%20products%2C%20including%20skin-lightening%20creams%20popular%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20fairness%20products%20market%20continues%20to%20generate%20substantial%20profits%2C%20seeing%20a%20growth%20rate%20of%205.4%25%20in%202023%2C%20concerns%20remain%20regarding%20consumer%20awareness%20about%20the%20potential%20side%20effects%20of%20such%20creams%2C%20which%20include%20skin%20damage%20and%20even%20poisoning%20due%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20mercury%2C%20melanin%2C%20and%20hydroquinone%20in%20certain%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChannamma%20Kambara%20of%20the%20Bengaluru-based%20Institute%20of%20Social%20and%20Economic%20Change%20observes%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20generation%20is%20comfortable%20in%20their%20own%20skin%20and%20are%20well-informed%20scientifically%20about%20the%20genes%20and%20melanin.%20They%20are%20more%20focused%20on%20other%20aspects%2C%20like%20glowing%20skin%2C%20bright%20and%20radiant%20skin%2C%20skin%20without%20breaks%2C%20etc.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EMillennials'%20Shifting%20Skincare%20Preferences%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20Eurocentric%20ideals%2C%20young%20Indians%20have%20also%20been%20influenced%20by%20the%20flawless%2C%20glass-like%20skin%20popularised%20in%20Korean%20culture.%20Exposure%20to%20K-dramas%2C%20South%20Korean%20pop%20stars%2C%20and%20actors%20with%20seemingly%20perfect%20skin%20have%20set%20such%20beauty%20standards.%20Consequently%2C%20the%20skincare%20industry%20has%20responded%20by%20emphasising%20%E2%80%98realistic'%20skincare%20regimens%20focused%20on%20cleansing%2C%20moisturising%2C%20sun%20protection%2C%20and%20addressing%20acne%20scars%20and%20hydration%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20new%20generation%20is%20focusing%20on%20skin%20health%20rather%20than%20fairness.%20They%20aspire%20for%20flawless%20Korean%20skin%20and%20follow%20some%20kind%20of%20skin%20regimen%20religiously.%20Those%20who%20are%20conscious%20about%20skin%20health%20are%20now%20investing%20in%20products%20like%20Vitamin%20C%20serum%2C%20anti-acne%20and%20anti-pimple%20products%2C%20face%20wash%2C%20sunscreen%2C%20face%20packs%2C%20etc.%C2%A0The%20availability%20of%20various%20brands%20and%20beauty%20products%20over%20the%20counter%20and%20online%20makes%20that%20easier%2C%E2%80%9D%20avers%20Ms.%C2%A0Kambara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20shift%20from%20%E2%80%98fairness'%20to%20%E2%80%98glow'%2C%20business%20interests%20of%20companies%20will%20likely%20sustain%20demand%20for%20such%20products.%20Efforts%20to%20change%20mindsets%20will%20require%20interventions%20at%20the%20educational%20level%2C%20leveraging%20the%20soft%20power%20of%20the%20Indian%20entertainment%20and%20advertising%20industries%2C%20and%20fostering%20conscious%20social%20movements%20to%20promote%20self-confidence%20that's%20rooted%20in%20inner%20qualities%20rather%20than%20external%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709106240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-07%2Fhbj2aeg8_fair-lovely-reuters_625x300_02_July_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffrom-fair-to-glow-is-indian-fixation-with-light-skin-finally-over-5142546%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20recent%20report%20by%20Nielsen%20indicates%20a%20decline%20of%203%25%20in%20the%20volume%20of%20fairness%20creams%20in%202023%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year.%20Does%20this%20indicate%20a%20shift%20in%20outlook%2C%20or%20something%20else%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffrom-fair-to-glow-is-indian-fixation-with-light-skin-finally-over-5142546%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffrom-fair-to-glow-is-indian-fixation-with-light-skin-finally-over-5142546%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffrom-fair-to-glow-is-indian-fixation-with-light-skin-finally-over-5142546%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Marriage%20Proposal%20%26quot%3BNot%20Reaching%20Desired%20End%26quot%3B%20Not%20Cheating%3A%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20recently%20dismissed%20a%20cheating%20case%20against%20a%20man%20who%20did%20not%20go%20through%20with%20a%20wedding%20after%20talks%20with%20the%20woman's%20family.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BThere%20can%20be%20multiple%20reasons%20for%20initiating%20a%20marriage%20proposal%20and%20then%20the%20proposal%20not%20reaching%20the%20desired%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20Justices%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20and%20Prasanna%20B%20Varale%20said%20while%20cancelling%20a%20case%20against%20Raju%20Krishna%20Shedbalkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaju%20Krishna%20Shedbalkar%20had%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20a%202021%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20order%20that%20held%20him%20guilty%20of%20cheating%20under%20Section%20417%2C%20which%20entails%20a%20jail%20term%20of%20up%20to%20one%20year%20or%20fine%2C%20or%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTime%20and%20again%2C%20this%20court%20has%20reiterated%20that%20in%20order%20to%20make%20out%20an%20offence%20under%20cheating%20the%20intention%20to%20cheat%20or%20deceive%20should%20be%20right%20from%20the%20beginning.%20By%20no%20stretch%20of%20imagination%2C%20this%20is%20even%20reflected%20from%20the%20complaint%20made%20by%20the%20informant%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20Raju%20Krishna%20Shedbalkar%2C%20his%20brothers%2C%20sister%20and%20mother%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20filed%20by%20a%20woman%20who%20alleged%20that%20he%20had%20cheated%20her%20by%20not%20marrying%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20alleged%20that%20her%20family%20had%20found%20Mr%20Shedbalkar%20suitable%20for%20her%2C%20and%20both%20had%20started%20talking%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20her%20father%20had%20also%20paid%20Rs%2075%2C000%20to%20book%20a%20wedding%20venue%2C%20but%20she%20learnt%20that%20Mr%20Shedbalkar%20had%20married%20someone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20had%20dismissed%20the%20case%20against%20all%20the%20accused%2C%20except%20Mr%20Shedbalkar.%20The%20High%20Court%20noted%20since%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Binduced%20the%20woman's%20father%20to%20book%20a%20marriage%20hall%2C%20there%20is%20prima%20facie%20material%20which%20makes%20out%20a%20case%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverturning%20that%20decision%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20there%20was%20no%20evidence%20to%20prove%20that%20the%20man%20had%20any%20intention%20to%20cheat%20the%20woman.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20possible%20theoretically%20yet%20in%20order%20to%20prove%20an%20offence%20of%20cheating%20in%20such%20cases%20prosecution%20must%20have%20reliable%20and%20trustworthy%20evidence%20in%20order%20to%20first%20prosecute%20such%20a%20case.%20There%20is%20no%20such%20evidence%20before%20the%20prosecution%20and%20therefore%20no%20offence%20under%20Section%20417%20is%20also%20made%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judges%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709106000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-09%2Fu9pd1cq8_marriage-generic-istock_625x300_11_September_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcheating-case-marriage-false-marriage-promise-supreme-court-marriage-proposal-not-reaching-desired-end-not-cheating-supreme-court-5142497%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20recently%20quashed%20a%20cheating%20case%20against%20a%20man%20who%20did%20not%20marry%20a%20woman%20despite%20being%20in%20talks%20with%20the%20complainant%20and%20her%20family.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcheating-case-ma