%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1684-hanuma-vihari-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHanuma%20Vihari%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bunder%20threat%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fstory%2Fhanuma-vihari-controversy-teammates-were-threatened-to-sign-letter-of-support-claims-aca-2507929-2024-02-27%5C%22%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Earlier.%20Vihari%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20ACA%20for%20'mistreatment'%20and%20said%20that%20he%20was%20asked%20to%20resign%20from%20captaincy%20after%20the%20first%20game%20of%20the%20season.%20He%20further%20alleged%20that%20his%20removal%20came%20after%20an%20altercation%20with%20a%20teammate%20who%20was%20the%20son%20of%20a%20politician.%20Vihari%20shared%20a%20copy%20of%20his%20statement%20on%20social%20media%20along%20with%20signatures%20of%20his%20teammates%20but%20the%20ACA%20has%20said%20that%20the%20cricketers%20were%20forced%20to%20sign%20it%20by%20the%20veteran%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHanuma%20Vihari%20has%20alleged%20that%20despite%20all%20the%20players%20in%20the%20team%20supporting%20him%20to%20continue%20as%20the%20captain%2C%20he%20was%20removed.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20the%20concerned%20players%20have%20complained%20to%20the%20Andhra%20Cricket%20Association%20against%20Vihari.%20Some%20players%20have%20complained%20to%20the%20Andhra%20Cricket%20Association%20that%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20sign%20under%20threats.%20Andhra%20Cricket%20Association%20will%20thoroughly%20investigate%20all%20the%20complaints%20received%20and%20report%20the%20facts%20to%20the%20BCCI%2C%26quot%3B%20ACA%20said%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Vihari)%20asked%20the%20Andhra%20Cricket%20Association%20to%20continue%20on%20behalf%20of%20Andhra%2C%20apologising%20for%20being%20emotional%20and%20frustrated%20for%20not%20being%20selected%20in%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%20as%20he%20was%20not%20given%20the%20NOC.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn