in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28111408%2FUntitled-design-10-2.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Two%20eminent%20writers%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20Sanskrit%20scholar%20Jagadguru%20Swami%20Rambhadracharya%20and%20renowned%20lyricist%20Sampooran%20Singh%20Kalra%2C%20better%20known%20as%20Gulzar%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20selected%20to%20receive%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20highest%20literary%20honour%2C%20the%20Jnanpith%20Award%2C%20this%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20award%2C%20usually%20awarded%20to%20only%20one%20litterateur%20per%20year%2C%20has%20sparked%20controversy%20whenever%20it%20has%20been%20awarded%20jointly.%20Shrilal%20Shukla%20and%20Amarkant%20were%20honoured%20together%2015%20years%20ago%20in%202009%20while%20Gurdial%20Singh%20shared%20the%20award%20with%20Nirmal%20Verma%20in%201999.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Jnanpith%20Award%20was%20instituted%20in%201965%20and%20is%20operated%20by%20the%20Jain%20family%20that%20runs%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20task%20of%20publication%20and%20awards%20is%20handled%20by%20a%20trust.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20latest%20announcement%20made%20for%20the%20Jnanpith%20Award%20for%202023%20echoes%20the%20much-hyped%20%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%99.%20The%20work%20of%20academies%20is%20often%20shadowed%20by%20governments.%C2%A0However%2C%20government%20interference%20is%C2%A0%20generally%20a%20hushed%20affair.%20However%2C%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20has%20sent%20ripples%20down%20the%20literary%20community.%20Questions%20are%20being%20raised%20about%20the%20integrity%20of%20Jnanpith%20with%20many%20wondering%20if%20it%20has%20chosen%20to%20compromise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDescribing%20Swami%20Rambhadracharya%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98renowned%20scholar%2C%20educationist%2C%20philosopher%2C%20preacher%20and%20religious%20leader%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20award%20committee%20has%20given%20details%20of%20his%20association%20with%20the%20Ramanand%20sect%20and%20his%20religious%20positions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20further%20stated%20that%20he%20knows%2022%20languages%2C%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98poet%20and%20writer%E2%80%99%20of%20many%20languages%20including%20Sanskrit%2C%20Hindi%2C%20Awadhi%2C%20and%20Maithili%2C%20and%20has%20authored%20more%20than%20240%20books.%20He%20is%20said%20to%20have%20composed%20four%20epics%2C%20two%20of%20which%20are%20in%20Hindi%2C%20and%20has%20written%20commentaries%20on%20religious%20texts%20and%20is%20a%20well-known%20expert%20on%20Tulsidas%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamcharitmanas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Modi%20government%20honoured%20him%20with%20Padma%20Vibhushan%20in%202015.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20fail%20to%20understand%20why%20the%20Jnanpith%20announcement%20did%20not%20mention%20that%20Swamiji%20has%20continuously%20faced%20physical%20challenges%20because%20he%20lost%20his%20eyesight%20when%20he%20was%20two%20months%20old.%20There%20is%20also%20no%20mention%20that%20he%20is%20close%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20who%20flew%20to%20Chitrakoot%20to%20inaugurate%20his%2010%2C000-page%20Ashtadhyay%20commentary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESwamiji%20had%20testified%20in%20favour%20of%20Ramlala%20Virajman%20in%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20dispute.%20He%20was%20among%20the%20initial%20%E2%80%98warriors%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%2C%20was%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20campaign%20to%20demolish%20the%20%E2%80%98tainted%20structure%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20went%20to%20jail%20too.%20He%20denigrates%20the%20leaders%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20Congress%20by%20name%20and%20calls%20them%20%E2%80%98fools%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20is%20also%20known%20to%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.india.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fswami-rambhadracharya-initiates-yagna-with-the-intention-of-reclaiming-pok-heaps-praises-for-pm-modi-6657842%2F%5C%22%3Econtroversial%20statements%20regarding%20Pakistan%20occupied%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%20(PoK).%20Recently%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20the%20guardian%20of%20Ramjanmabhoomi%20Pranpratistha.%20He%20retaliated%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqkSAOYTSgYo%5C%22%3EJyotirmoy%20Shankaracharya%20for%20calling%20the%20%3Cem%3Epratishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%20not%20scriptural%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20temple%20trust%20also%20kept%20reiterating%20that%20the%20consecration%20is%20taking%20place%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20Ramanandi%20sect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20tried%20to%20sift%20through%20online%20sources%20to%20search%20Swamiji%E2%80%99s%20work%20and%20found%20one%20of%20his%20partly%20Hindi%20poems%20which%20has%20been%20translated%20into%20English%20and%20Russian%20by%20a%20foreign%20disciple%20of%20his.%20The%20entire%20poem%2C%20which%20is%20Swamiji%E2%80%99s%20version%20of%20one%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamcharitmanas%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20quotes%2C%20is%20available%20on%20Swamiji%E2%80%99s%20official%20Facebook%20page.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20admit%20that%20I%20have%20not%20read%20the%20Sanskrit%20or%20Hindi%20literary%20works%20of%20Swami%20Rambhadracharya.%20However%2C%20I%20did%20listen%20to%20one%20of%20his%20sermons%20on%20YouTube%20and%20it%20failed%20to%20impress%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20compiled%20lectures%20(not%20writings)%20of%20speakers%20like%20Swami%20Akhandanand%2C%20Swami%20Ramsukhdas%2C%20Acharya%20Tulsi%20and%20Maulana%20Waheeduddin%20Khan%20were%20far%20more%20convincing.%20Rajneesh-Osho%E2%80%99s%20storytelling%20is%20also%20full%20of%20literary%20quotes%20and%20jokes.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20does%20not%20seem%20logical%20to%20pit%20a%20saint%2C%20who%20was%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20temple%20movement%2C%20against%20literary%20figures%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20sermons%20or%20commentary.%20This%20is%20disrespectful%20even%20of%20a%20saint.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIronically%2C%20Swamiji%E2%80%99s%20nomination%20for%20the%20Jnanpith%20award%20was%20welcomed%20not%20by%20the%20literary%20community%20but%20by%20controversial%20figures%20like%20Baba%20Bageshwar%20Dham%20and%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leader%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chauhan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnames-of-indira-and-nargis-dropped-from-national-film-awards%5C%22%3E%20Names%20of%20%E2%80%98Indira%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Nargis%E2%80%99%20Dropped%20From%20National%20Film%20Awards%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%20Gulzar%2C%20the%20second%20nominee%20for%20the%20Jnanpith%2C%20is%20a%20prominent%20personality%20of%20Hindi%20cinema.%20He%20is%20a%20successful%20filmmaker%20who%20has%20made%20many%20interesting%20films%20and%20has%20expertise%20in%20scriptwriting%20and%20songs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20received%20the%20Filmfare%20Award%2022%20times%2C%20National%20Film%20Award%20six%20times%2C%20Dadasaheb%20Phalke%20Award%2C%20Padma%20Bhushan%20and%20even%20a%20Grammy%20and%20Oscar%20(with%20AR%20Rahman)%20for%20song-writing.%20He%20is%20a%20popular%20cine-lyricist%20and%20his%20poetry%20gained%20great%20fame%20after%20receiving%20the%20Sahitya%20Akademi%20Award%20for%20an%20Urdu%20short%20story%20collection%20in%202002.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20he%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20popular%20face%20of%20literature%20festivals%20in%20Jaipur%20and%20other%20cities.%20The%20series%20of%20so-called%20literary%20festivals%20has%20set%20up%20a%20market%20with%20mainly%20English%20publishers%2C%20writers%E2%80%99%20agents%20and%20renowned%20writers%2C%20politicians%2C%20actors%2C%20singers%2C%20and%20anchors.%20The%20market%20itself%20bears%20their%20expenses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20the%20glittering%20world%20of%20cinema%2C%20in%20these%20%E2%80%98literary%E2%80%99%20fairs%20too%2C%20people%20are%20more%20interested%20in%20getting%20a%20glimpse%20of%20popular%20figures%2C%20taking%20selfies%20with%20them%20or%20displaying%20their%20fashion%20sense%2C%20rather%20than%20expressing%20their%20love%20for%20literature%20(or%20rather%20books%2C%20because%20even%20a%20cookery%20book%20can%20be%20%E2%80%98launched%E2%80%99%20there).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20only%20concern%20is%20that%20perhaps%20the%20semblance%20of%20lit-fests%20has%20started%20influencing%20serious%20literary%20awards.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20been%20reading%20Gulzar%20sahab%20ever%20since%20his%20poetry%20collection%20was%20published%20in%20Hindi%20by%20his%20best%20friend%20Bhushan%20Banmali%20in%20the%201970s.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20romantic%20literature%20of%20Urdu%20and%20Punjabi%20had%20its%20own%20charm.%20But%20later%2C%20after%20the%20emotional%20phase%20of%20songs%20like%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EJab%20bhi%20ye%20dil%20udaas%20hota%2C%20Jaane%20kaun%20aas%20paas%20hota%20hai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EShaam%20ki%20aankh%20mein%20nami%20si%20hai%2C%20aaj%20phir%20aap%20ki%20kami%20si%20hai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20some%20deep%20poetry%20was%20felt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20yearning%20never%20ceased.%20The%20turmoil%20of%20society%20and%20politics%20did%20not%20become%20the%20concern%20of%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eghazals%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20poems.%20Even%20in%20romanticism%2C%20there%20was%20reiteration%20in%20different%20forms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBharatiya%20Jnanpith%20mentioned%20Swamiji%E2%80%99s%20birthplace%20as%20Jaunpur%20in%20its%20announcement%20but%20Gulzar%20sahab%E2%80%99s%20birthplace%20(Dina%2C%20Pakistan)%20was%20left%20out.%20In%20the%20introduction%2C%20his%20identity%20as%20an%20Urdu%20poet%20has%20been%20downplayed%20and%20mentioned%20only%20after%20Hindi.%20The%20introduction%20goes%3A%20%E2%80%98Sampooran%20Singh%20Kalra%2C%20popularly%20known%20as%20Gulzar%2C%20is%20a%20famous%20lyricist%20of%20Hindi%20films.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20he%20is%20a%20poet%2C%20screenwriter%2C%20film%20director%2C%20playwright%20and%20a%20famous%20poet.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20works%20are%20mainly%20in%20Hindi%2C%20Urdu%20and%20Punjabi%E2%80%A6%20Gulzar%20has%20been%20setting%20new%20milestones%20in%20the%20field%20of%20literature.%20In%20poetry%2C%20he%20invented%20a%20new%20genre%20%E2%80%9CTriveni%E2%80%9D%20which%20is%20a%20non-mukaffa%20poem%20of%20three%20lines.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrivenis%20were%20regularly%20published%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESarika%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20when%20Kamleshwar%20was%20the%20editor.%20Gulzar%20used%20to%20give%20the%20third%20verse%20a%20shocking%20twist%20which%20became%20like%20a%20game%20at%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20he%20is%20a%20good%20man%2C%20an%20accomplished%20filmmaker%20and%20a%20popular%20lyricist%2C%20there%20are%20more%20profound%20creators%20in%20literature%20than%20him.%20There%20has%20been%20some%20discussion%20on%20social%20media%20about%20this%2C%20though%20not%20enough.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHindi%20poet%20and%20editor%20Vishnu%20Nagar%20posted%20on%20Facebook%20that%20the%20neglect%20of%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Shukla%2C%20and%20other%20writers%20who%20have%20done%20great%20work%20and%20carved%20a%20niche%20in%20Hindi%20fiction%2C%20poetry%20and%20children%E2%80%99s%20literature%2C%20is%20disappointing.%20However%2C%20apart%20from%20Hindi%2C%20many%20prominent%20writers%20in%20other%20Indian%20languages%20are%20still%20beyond%20the%20realm%20of%20Jnanpith.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECritic%20Shambhunath%20has%20called%20it%20the%20%E2%80%98downfall%20of%20the%20Jnanpith%20Award%E2%80%99.%20Virendra%20Yadav%20believes%20that%20the%20devaluation%20of%20Jnanpith%20began%20when%20Shahryar%20was%20handed%20the%20award%20by%20Amitabh%20Bachchan.%20%E2%80%98In%20status%2C%20it%20has%20now%20become%20like%20a%20dustbin%E2%80%99s%20beauty.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20reading%20%E2%80%98lyricist%20Gulzar%E2%80%99%20written%20in%20the%20release%20of%20Jnanpith%20press%20release%2C%20writers%20began%20comparing%20the%20announcement%20with%20Bob%20Dylan%20getting%20the%20Nobel%20Prize.%20It%20does%20not%20seem%20appropriate%20at%20all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20his%20time%2C%20Dylan%20had%20shaken%20the%20conservative%20mentality%20of%20America%20with%20ideological%20excitement.%20Paired%20with%20American%20traditional%20music%2C%20his%20songs%20created%20a%20new%20political%20idiom.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBob%20Dylan%20raised%20his%20voice%20in%20favour%20of%20freedom%2C%20peace%20and%20justice.%20He%20wrote%20against%20war%2C%20nuclear%20threat%2C%20racism%20and%20slavery%2C%20sang%20against%20contempt%20and%20violence%20against%20the%20African-American%20community%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20whites%2C%20stood%20in%20support%20of%20protesters%20and%20their%20demonstrations%20in%20his%20compositions%20and%20gave%20strength%20to%20the%20voice%20of%20civil%20rights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDylan%2C%20in%20his%20entirety%2C%20was%20a%20voice%20of%20resistance.%20American%20society%20was%20in%20dire%20need%20of%20voices%20that%20could%20call%20out%20and%20say%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20and%20how%20many%20times%20must%20a%20man%20look%20up%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20he%20can%20see%20the%20sky%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20how%20many%20ears%20must%20one%20man%20have%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20he%20can%20hear%20people%20cry%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20and%20how%20many%20deaths%20will%20it%20take%20%E2%80%99til%20he%20knows%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20too%20many%20people%20have%20died%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20answer%2C%20my%20friend%2C%20is%20blowing%20in%20the%20wind!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20respect%20Gulzar%20%3Cem%3Esahab%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20an%20evergreen%20filmmaker%20and%20he%20is%20very%20fond%20of%20me.%20We%20often%20have%20many%20long%20chats%20regarding%20Kedarji%20(late%20Kedarnath%20Singh)%20and%20lit-fests.%20But%20i%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3En%20my%2050%20years%20of%20journalism%20and%2035%20as%20editor%20%E2%80%93%20where%20I%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20publishing%20a%20vast%20amount%20of%20literature%20in%20Hindi%20which%20required%20a%20close%20reading%20%E2%80%93%20I%20never%20saw%20Gulzar%20sahab%20taking%20on%20transformative%20concern%20and%20talk%20of%20the%20ills%20of%20society%20and%20politics%20in%20his%20songs.%20Romanticism%20can%20bring%20joy%20but%20after%20a%20certain%20period%20it%20becomes%20dull.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20not%20necessary%20that%20a%20courageous%20attitude%20in%20the%20subject%20one%20writes%20about%20would%20do%20away%20with%20the%20shortcomings%20of%20the%20craft.%20Only%20after%20such%20works%20get%20published%20can%20learned%20critics%20decide%20how%20much%20of%20it%20is%20poetry%20and%20how%20much%20is%20noise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGulzar%20would%20also%20agree%20that%20there%20are%20poets%20among%20us%20who%20write%20in%20different%20languages%20of%20the%20country%2C%20who%20have%20a%20stronger%20claim%20on%20the%20literary%20scale.%20By%20honouring%20them%2C%20the%20awards%20will%20gain%20recognition%20and%20credibility%20and%20boost%20their%20own%20pride.%20The%20rich%20tradition%20of%20Jnanpith%20has%20been%20no%20different%20but%20the%20recent%20turn%20of%20events%20has%20left%20it%20in%20darkness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20it%20is%20the%20era%20of%20%E2%80%98New%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20in%20which%20lyricists%2C%20stage%20poets%2C%20storytellers%20(one%20can%20even%20find%20all%20these%20qualities%20in%20one%20person)%20are%20awarded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAwards%20are%20not%20offered%20but%20procured%20nowadays.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fom-thanvi%5C%22%3EOm%20Thanvi%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20who%20retired%20as%20editor%20of%20Jansatta%2C%20a%20Hindi%20daily%20of%20the%20Indian%20Express%20group%2C%20in%202015.%20He%20was%20the%20founding%20Vice%20Chancellor%20of%20HJ%20University%20of%20Journalism%20and%20Mass%20Communication%2C%20Jaipur.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F268702%2Fjnanpith-award-film-director-and-lyricist-gulzar-sanskrit-scholar-rambhadracharya%2F%5C%22%3EHindi%20orginal%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709103756000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28111408%2FUntitled-design-10-2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fgulzar-jagadguru-swami-rambhadracharya-and-the-downfall-of-the-jnanpith-award%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Questions%20are%20being%20raised%20about%20the%20integrity%20of%20Jnanpith%20after%20the%20announcement%20of%20this%20year's%20recipients%2C%20with%20many%20wondering%20if%20it%20has%20chosen%20to%20compromise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fg