e%20majority%20mark%20of%2035%20in%20the%2068-member%20state%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20nine%20MLAs%20%E2%80%93%20six%20of%20Congress%20and%20three%20independents%20%E2%80%93%20cross%20voted%20for%20BJP%20in%20Tuesday%E2%80%99s%20Rajya%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20Congress%20government%20is%20technically%20now%20one%20short%20of%20the%20majority%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MLAs%20who%20cross%20voted%20include%20Rajinder%20Rana%2C%20Sudhir%20Sharma%2C%20Ravi%20Thakur%2C%20Inder%20Dutt%20Lakhanpal%2C%20Chaitanya%20Sharma%20and%20Devender%20Bhutto%20while%20the%20independents%20are%20K.L.%20Thakur%2C%20Hoshiyar%20Singh%20and%20Ashish%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20Congress%20MLAs%2C%20as%20BJP%20claims%2C%20are%20sitting%20on%20the%20fence%2C%20ready%20to%20switch%20sides%20as%20they%20were%20unhappy%20with%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20current%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20who%20cross-voted%20are%20all%20incommunicado%20since%20casting%20their%20votes.%20As%20per%20media%20reports%2C%20they%20were%20first%20taken%20to%20Panchkula%20in%20Haryana%20late%20on%20Tuesday%20evening.%20They%20were%20reportedly%20accompanied%20by%20the%20three%20independents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20video%20footages%20released%20by%20section%20of%20media%2C%20these%20MLAs%20were%20shown%20leaving%20Panchkula%20hotel%20some%20time%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20developing%20story%20and%20will%20be%20updated%20as%20news%20comes%20in.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709094076000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28094910%2F428690237_960701998744531_951321776277677293_n.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhimachal-bjp-congress-coup-independents-governor%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20state%20CM%20and%20BJP%20leader%20met%20the%20Himachal%20Governor%20to%20ask%20for%20a%20floor%20test%20ahead%20of%20the%20budget%20session%