%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-hamas-war-bidens-hopes-for-ceasefire-by-end-of-weekend-are-wishful-thinking-hamas-tells-sky-news-13082400%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20jails%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%20winner%20for%20'repeatedly%20criticising%20armed%20forces'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709054340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-oleg-orlov-russian_6471294.jpg%3F20240227175547%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Foleg-orlov-russia-jails-nobel-peace-prize-winner-for-repeatedly-criticising-armed-forces-13082387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Oleg%20Orlov%20has%20spent%20his%20life%20documenting%20repression.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A74%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Foleg-orlov-russia-jails-nobel-peace-prize-winner-for-repeatedly-criticising-armed-forces-13082387%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Foleg-orlov-russia-jails-nobel-peace-prize-winner-for-repeatedly-criticising-armed-forces-13082387%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Foleg-orlov-russia-jails-nobel-peace-prize-winner-for-repeatedly-criticising-armed-forces-13082387%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Himachal%20Pradesh%3A%20Ruling%20Congress%20Suffers%20Jolt%2C%20Loses%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Election%20to%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F49_Image8.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20a%20shocking%20political%20development%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20ruling%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20lost%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Harsh%20Mahajan%20despite%20the%20Congress%20enjoying%20a%20comfortable%20majority%20in%20the%20state%20assembly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20leaders%20who%20were%20present%20during%20the%20voting%20suggested%20that%20nine%20lawmakers%2C%20including%20seven%20party%20MLAs%20and%20two%20independents%20supporting%20the%20party%2C%20refrained%20from%20showing%20their%20ballot%20papers%20to%20their%20polling%20agents%2C%20leading%20to%20speculation%20that%20they%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20Mahajan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20candidates%20secured%2034%20votes%20each%20in%20the%2068-member%20state%20assembly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVictory%20tilted%20towards%20Mahajan%20after%20a%20draw%20of%20lots%20was%20held%20as%20a%20tie-breaker.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20Himachal%20CM%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20targeted%20the%20BJP%20for%20its%20alleged%20horse%20trading%20and%20intimidation%20of%20Congress%20MLAs%2C%20the%20final%20result%20was%20big%20a%20blow%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20had%20a%20strength%20of%2040%20MLAs%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20and%20the%20additional%20support%20of%20three%20independent%20MLAs%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20total%20strength%20of%2025%20MLAs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20victory%20is%20even%20more%20detrimental%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20former%20BJP%20Himachal%20CM%20Jai%20Ram%20Thakur%E2%80%99s%20claim%20that%20the%20Sukhu%20government%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20a%20minority%20in%20the%20house%20and%20that%20the%20BJP%20plans%20to%20bring%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20in%20the%20ongoing%20budget%20session%20in%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20speculation%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20bring%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20him%2C%20Sukhu%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20see%20when%20the%20assembly%20session%20commences%20%E2%80%A6%20those%20who%20have%20cross-voted%20are%20being%20asked%20by%20their%20families%20why%20they%20did%20this.%20So%2C%20if%20the%20families%20are%20asking%20them%2C%20then%20maybe%20a%20few%20of%20them%20would%20think%20about%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eghar%20wapasi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5BHindi%20for%20%E2%80%98returning%20home%E2%80%99%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20Sukhu%20alleged%20that%20a%20convoy%20comprising%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20and%20Haryana%20Police%20personnel%20took%20away%20five%20or%20six%20Congress%20MLAs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMahajan%20told%20the%20media%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20state%20government%20is%20in%20the%20minority%20right%20now.%20Fence-sitters%20in%20the%20government%20are%20ready%20to%20come%20to%20this%20side.%20They%20are%20unhappy%20with%20the%20government.%20They%20are%20so%20upset%20that%20they%20can%20do%20anything.%20This%20government%20won%E2%80%99t%20go%20on%2C%20it%20will%20topple%20with%20its%20own%20weight.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20indicated%20that%20suspense%20is%20not%20over%20in%20Himachal%E2%80%99s%20politics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%20in%20a%20first%20reaction%2C%20Singhvi%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20of%20all%2C%20I%20extend%20heartiest%20congratulations%20to%20Harsh%20Mahajan.%20But%20I%20would%20like%20to%20tell%20his%20party%2C%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20introspect%20and%20think.%20When%20a%2025-member%20party%20fields%20a%20candidate%20against%20a%2043-member%20party%2C%20there%20is%20just%20one%20message%20%E2%80%93%20we%20will%20shamelessly%20do%20everything%20which%20is%20not%20permitted%20by%20the%20law%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20be%20living%20in%20a%20fool%E2%80%99s%20paradise%20if%20we%20think%20that%20alll%20those%20MLAs%20%5Bwho%20cross-voted%5D%20had%20a%20sudden%20change%20of%20heart%20due%20to%20some%20ideology%20or%20new%20policy.%20This%20is%20rather%20disappointing%20and%20something%20this%20hilly%20state%20has%20never%20seen%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singhvi%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Mahajan%20dedicated%20his%20victory%20to%20top%20BJP%20leaders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20opposition%20Jai%20Ram%20Thakur%20will%20reportedly%20meet%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20governor%20tomorrow%20and%20has%20sought%20Sukhu%E2%80%99s%20resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMany%20aspect%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20defeat%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20has%20many%20aspects.%20Some%20speculate%20that%20it%20was%20the%20outcome%20of%20infighting%20between%20Sukhu%20and%20Himachal%20Congress%20chief%20Pratibha%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20wife%20of%20the%20late%20Congress%20stalwart%20Virbhadra%20Singh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20polls%2C%20Pratibha%20staked%20a%20claim%20on%20the%20CM%20post%2C%20which%20went%20to%20Sukhu%20as%20the%20Congress%20went%20for%20a%20generation%20shift%20after%20eight-time%20CM%20Virbhadra%E2%80%99s%20death.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20then%2C%20their%20differences%20have%C2%A0%20cropped%20up%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20several%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20speculation%20becomes%20more%20rife%20because%20most%20MLAs%20who%20cross-voted%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20favour%20were%20once%20staunch%20supporters%20of%20Virbhadra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20people%20also%20believed%20that%20some%20MLAs%20were%20upset%20with%20Sukhu%20for%20not%20giving%20them%20plum%20postings%20in%20the%20government%20and%20that%20these%20MLAs%20had%20humiliated%20the%20party%2C%20especially%20in%20light%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20are%20round%20the%20corner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20this%2C%20Mahajan%20%E2%80%93%20the%20winning%20candidate%20%E2%80%93%20is%20an%20old%20Congress%20veteran