ical%20condition%20of%20the%20petitioner.%20It%20is%20submitted%20that%20the%20record%20will%20reveal%20the%20report%20is%20not%20correct%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20apex%20court%20bench%20of%20Justices%20B.R.%20Gavai%20and%20Sandeep%20Mehta%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CTaking%20into%20consideration%20all%20this%2C%20it%20will%20be%20appropriate%20that%20the%20medical%20condition%20is%20examined%20by%20a%20board%20appointed%20by%20the%20AIIMS%20director.%20The%20board%20shall%20also%20consider%20the%20jail%20records%20%5Band%20the%5D%20complete%20medical%20history%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20petitioner.%20List%20after%20two%20weeks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERejecting%20the%20argument%20of%20additional%20solicitor%20general%20S.V.%20Raju%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Delhi%20police%2C%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20founder%20was%20asking%20for%20special%20treatment%2C%20the%20bench%20underlined%20that%20if%20Asaram%20Bapu%20could%20get%20medical%20treatment%20at%20AIIMS%2C%20then%20Purkayastha%20could%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fweeks-after-unprecedented-raids-newsclick-staffers-grapple-with-waiting-game%5C%22%3ENewsClick%3A%20Govt%20Impunity%20Caused%20Seizure%20of%20as%20Many%20as%20250%20Devices%2C%20Paralysing%20Work%20of%2090%20Journalists%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20convict%20in%20Jodhpur%20(Asaram)%20who%20keeps%20getting%20medical%20treatment%20at%20AIIMS%20%E2%80%A6%20you%20can%20release%20him%20and%20then%20he%20can%20get%20treated%20wherever%20he%20wants%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judges%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20Sibal%2C%20appearing%20for%20Purkayastha%2C%20highlighted%20in%20the%20court%20that%20his%20client%20%E2%80%9Cshould%20not%20pass%20away%20while%20they%20%5Bthe%20additional%20solicitor%20genera%5D%