ndia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-2-1708521951-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342786%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERaghuveer%20has%20developed%20a%20unique%20scalp%20cooling%20system%20that%20alleviates%20the%20trauma%20of%20chemotherapy-induced%20hair%20loss.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remembered%20the%20experience%20of%20my%20aunt%20when%20she%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20ovarian%20cancer.%20I%20saw%20her%20losing%20confidence%20and%20being%20unable%20to%20get%20by%20with%20her%20life.%20That%20really%20triggered%20me.%20I%20started%20looking%20for%20solutions%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20came%20across%20the%20scalp%20cooling%20method%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%2034-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20availability%20of%20scalp%20cooling%20devices%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20company%20had%20made%20silicon-based%20caps%20that%20come%20in%20three%20different%20sizes%20%E2%80%94%20small%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20large.%20The%20disadvantage%20of%20such%20caps%20is%20that%20they%20cannot%20fit%20all%20kinds%20of%20scalps%20perfectly%2C%20as%20scalps%20have%20a%20very%20complicated%20anatomical%20structure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChemotherapy%20destroys%20all%20fast-growing%20cells%20like%20cancerous%20tumours.%20Along%20with%20this%2C%20it%20also%20destroys%20fast-growing%20hair%20follicles%20as%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20differentiate%20between%20healthy%20and%20cancerous%20cells.%20So%2C%20if%20the%20cap%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20fit%20properly%2C%20then%20the%20entire%20scalp%20will%20not%20be%20cooled%2C%20causing%20high%20chances%20of%20hair%20loss%20in%20that%20area.%20This%20destroys%20the%20main%20purpose%20of%20the%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20Raghuveer%20decided%20to%20design%20a%20cap%20that%20could%20accommodate%20all%20head%20sizes.%20In%202020%2C%20he%20